{"tid":663871,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［急］召喚做幼教的巴絲","createTime":"2018-05-13T15:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T00:28:30.000Z","uid":113546,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"736771e73880d27cfb1ae4a9767e92883f958132","tid":663871,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:48:23.000Z","msg":"朋友今年畢業<br />\n見左幾間幼稚園<br />\n依家收到一間私校嘅offer 過多幾日就要覆<br />\n<br />\n但佢煩惱緊做私校定大校好<br />\n佢覺得做大校學到嘅嘢會多好多<br />\n同時可以磨練到自己<br />\n希望有進步同突破<br />\n<br />\n同時將來想轉做私校 或者轉行<br />\n個籌碼都多啲<br />\n<br />\n因為我唔熟大校同私校嘅分別<br />\n我覺得私校好似人工高啲 <br />\n工作量冇大校咁多<br />\n<br />\n咁多位巴打絲打有咩意見？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5cb63107f54d0e123f2b27c014109cd747422f2","tid":663871,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:50:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3983a583fe7955cb2fd3442ee68ca0224c41fdd6","tid":663871,"uid":79077,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d4311b1ed8f55ea65751f5b987fa406c274b03b","tid":663871,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:52:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e596e85e4e87b68ef19848e20485be699423dd97","tid":663871,"uid":114735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:52:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af4d5a40f054b9b56c9f623feb2715f91aeeeb75","tid":663871,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3983a583fe7955cb2fd3442ee68ca0224c41fdd6","tid":663871,"uid":79077,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:52:43.000Z","msg":"個朋友女仔嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打幫推"},{"pid":"247ae1015010ed70be05e96b8957034cd7b0ddec","tid":663871,"uid":17907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:53:21.000Z","msg":"做私校人工高？邊個講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2891bf3409d9e65bff16ac8e8e2e7d07e63b8b3","tid":663871,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e596e85e4e87b68ef19848e20485be699423dd97","tid":663871,"uid":114735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:52:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:55:10.000Z","msg":"其實有啲咩要學？<br />\n大校會唔會恰啲新人<br />\n表面比嘢你學<br />\n實則喺比啲豬骨頭你做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我有朋友嘅家組做過幼稚園<br />\n佢話除左本身嘅工作量大之外<br />\n<br />\n應付家長 <br />\n同啲老女人同事嘅人際關係最惡啃<br />\n<br />\n私校嘅人際關係會唔會好啲"},{"pid":"912a9924b2c036248eba472e5e6428b3a63cddf6","tid":663871,"uid":17907,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:55:34.000Z","msg":"做完私校hea到出唔返黎做其他<br />\n驚大校辛苦咪搵下細機構 不過相對資源會少啲<br />\n做完私校出黎搵返其他學校會難啲"},{"pid":"d0ebc940926a8e18ca8e603b2467a51ce4130f04","tid":663871,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"247ae1015010ed70be05e96b8957034cd7b0ddec","tid":663871,"uid":17907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:53:21.000Z","msg":"做私校人工高？邊個講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"其實喺我鳩up<br />\n感覺私校會高啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原諒我嘅無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ded0be9b2c362e504c80cae249e088f4861bfa","tid":663871,"u